{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1707-07_160","head":{"value":"Stances irrégulières","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juillet 1707 [tome 7], p. 160-164.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"La bataille d’Almanza ayant attiré des loüanges de toute l’Europe à Monsieur le Maréchal Duc de Berwick, les Ennemis même n’en ayant pû refuser à sa valeur &amp; à sa conduite ; Monsieur Trotebois, Avocat-Secretaire de la Ville de Toulon, a fait les Vers suivans à la gloire de ce Maréchal.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"value":"STANCES IRREGULIERES.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label"}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jaloux du bonheur de l’Espagne,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Assez &amp; trop long-tems, le Démon des Combats,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Avoit à sa fureur, immolé nos Soldats,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et fait à nos dépens, triompher l’Allemagne.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Des peuples ennemis des Rois,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Excitoient des mutins, le superbe courage ;","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et sans respect des plus saints droits,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Portoient jusqu’aux Autels, leur infernale rage.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais un Prince cheri des Cieux,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Traînant aprés luy, la Victoire,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Par des Exploits d’éternelle memoire,","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vange dans un seul jour, &amp; les Rois &amp; les Dieux.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#[0]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Barwick","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":", ","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#[2]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"ce Heros invincible,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#[3]/hi/#"}}}]},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Porte en tous lieux, la mort, l’épouvante &amp; l’horreur.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui pourroit resister à sa juste fureur ?","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La pieté l’anime, &amp; luy rend tout possible.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Anglois &amp; Portugais, Bataves &amp; Germains,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous estes massacrez, abattus, mis en fuite.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais rien n’échape à sa poursuite :","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Digues, Remparts, tout cede à l’effort de ses mains.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tel &amp; plus fort qu’Hercule, il a purgé l’Espagne,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De monstres affamez, &amp; de cruels Tyrans.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Car sans borner sa course au pied d’une Montagne,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il entreprend encor des travaux bien plus grands.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"#":{"value":" ","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"},"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il va chercher plus loin, des Conquestes nouvelles,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il va la foudre en main, par des faits inouïs,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Apprendre aux Etrangers, comme aux sujets rebelles,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"À redouter par tout, &amp; PHILIPE &amp; LOUIS.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/hi/#"}}}]}}]}}}